
# Products

## Product Object
Represents a product object.

```json
{
  "id": "prd_wpgnildbgg50k5u",
  "external_id": "4169648570416",
  "universal_id": "shopify:4169648570416",
  "platform": {
    "id": "eplat_5lu3ll5pgpumqvl",
    "name": "Shopify",
    "key": "shopify",
    "type": "PREDEFINED"
  },
  "name": "Dry Gin",
  "url": "https://onvoard-sample.myshopify.com/products/long-sleeve-t-shirt",
  "price": 75.0,
  "compare_at_price": 100.0,
  "currency": "SGD",
  "price_with_currency": "S$75",
  "compare_at_price_with_currency": "S$100",
  "created_timestamp": 1591045655,
  "group": {
    "id": "pdgrp_uwe83f1n4c58z0z",
    "name": "Beers"
  },
  "tags": [{
      "id": "prdtag_phdfnbtamnkypp8",
      "name": "tag-1"
    },
    {
      "id": "prdtag_4rp64333hegzv1s",
      "name": "tag-2"
    }
  ],
  "image_media": {
    "id": "file_b027hj4e3483rhi",
    "file_url": "https://storage.googleapis.com/onvoard/upload/product/image-media/4dc8b25e1275d2836b7b.jpeg",
    "created_timestamp": 1591045652,
    "height": 1280,
    "width": 1920
  }
}
```

### Attributes
Field | Type | Description
--------- | ------- | -----------
id | string | Unique identifier for the object.
external_id | string | Unique identifier for product in external platform.
universal_id | string | Unique identifier for product in the format `[platform_key].[external_id]`. For example, `shopify:12345`.
platform | object ([Ecommerce Platform Object](#ecommerce-platforms-ecommerce-platform-object)) | Platform associated with product.
name | string | Name of product.
url | string | URL for product.
price | float | The price of the product.
compare_at_price | float | The original price before discount.
currency | string | The three-letter currency code (ISO 4217 format) for product's price.
price_with_currency | string | Formatted price with currency in string like `CA$5,200.20`. Will be empty if either price or currency is not specified.
compare_at_price_with_currency | string | Formatted compare at price with currency. Will be empty if either compare_at_price or currency is not specified.
created_timestamp | integer | Timestamp when product was added to our system.
group | object ([Product Group Object](#products-product-group-object)) | Group for product.
tags[] | object array ([Product Tag Object](#products-product-tag-object)) | List of tags assigned to product.
image_media | object ([Image Media Object](#data-types-image-media-object)) | Image for product.


